title: How do I set network parameters?
answer:
When you insert a SIM card to your phone, the APN automatically set network parameters. 

 To view the network parameters, touch Settings > Mobile networks > Access Point Names. 

 When the network parameters are incorrect, touch ![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110863) > Reset to default.
